  "keyFeatures": [
    "JWT-based authentication with role-based access control (Administrador, Operador, Tecnico)",
    "Full CRUD for insurance claim expedientes with status lifecycle tracking",
    "File evidence uploads stored locally per expediente, organized by siniestro number",
    "Damage survey (levantamiento de daños) with line-item cost concepts and total cost calculation",
    "Aseguradora (insurer) management with seeded default data",
    "mDNS/Bonjour service discovery for LAN deployments",
    "Periodic system health checks for backend, database, disk, and evidence storage",
    "Structured logging to console and rotating log file"
  ],
